quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe Mum on tun mawnii O …óuu…óii mo∆¥∆¥ere Alla nde, ko Kanko woni hattan…óo kala huunde. Alaa ko ronki≈ãta Mo."
  67,2,"On tagir…óo maayde e nguurdam, fii ndaarndagol on onon …ìee yim…ìe, annda ko hommbo e mo'on …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude golle. Ko Kanko woni Foolu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Haforanoowo kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  67,3,"O tagu…óo kammuuli jee…ói…ói, kammu kala hino dewtii e hoore nguya ko aldaa e momondirgol hakkunde majji. An ndaaroowo on, a yi'ataa e ko …ìuradata woo e tagu Allah ngun. Yiltii gite maa …óen ndaaraa. Taw si a yi'ay ceekol maa …ìurdal? Pellet, a yi'ataa …óum ! Ko yi'aa, ko tagu √±e√±aangu, gollii ngu."
  67,4,"Refti ruttitin ndaar…óe maa …óen laa…ìi …ói…ói, gite …óen ruttitoray e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, tawde …óe yi'ataa ella ma ≈ãakkere e tagugol kammu ngun, hara kadi ko …óe ta∆¥ii…óe e ndaarugol."
  67,5,"Gom…óii Men cu…óirii kammu ngu aduna ngun koode jalbu…óe, Men wa…ói …óen koode fi…óir…óe seytanuuji wujjay…ói he…óoo …óin ko sunna …ói, Men hebilani …ìe ka laakara ton lette Yiite Hu…ì…ìunge."
  67,6,"√ëalnde Darngal, hino woodani …ìen yeddu…ìe Joomi mun, lette Yiite Jahnnama. Nge bonii ruttorde jaa∆¥oytee…ìe e magge."
  67,7,"Si wonii …ìe bugaama ka nder Yiite, …ìe naniraynge hito kaanungo sanne, hara hinge fatira wa ko wulnata."
  67,8,"Hinge e…ì…ìa fultagol, nge sennditoo, hakkee ko nge tikkani naadaa…óo e magge …ìen. Tuma kala nde fedde e heefer…ìe …ìen bugaa e magge, Malaa'ikaa…ìe ayninaa…ìe nge …ìen lamndoo …ìe wi'a: Enee ! Nulaa…óo araano e mon aduna, jertinaynoo…óo on e lette Allah …óen?"
  67,9,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'a : Ko pellet, Nulaa…óo aruno e amen tigi, himo jertinaynoo men e lette Allah …óen, kono men fenni mo, men wi'i mo: Allah jippinaali hay wahayu. Onon …ìee Nulaa…ìe, on wonaali si wanaa e nder majjere mawnde wo…ó…óii goonga."
  67,10,"Heefer…ìe …ìen wi'ita : Si men nanayno men ja…ìa, maa hara men haqqilayno men senndindira hakkunde goonga e meere, men jeyetanooke e yim…ìe Yiite …ìen; men gom…óinayno Nulaa…ìe …ìen, men goongina ko …ìe addi kon, fii no men jeyiree e yim…ìe Aljanna …ìen."
  67,11,"∆Åe qirritanoo ko'e-ma…ì…ìe, keeferaaku e fennugol …ìe ngol, Yiite ngen jojji e ma…ì…ìe. Awa halakuyee woodanii yim…ìe Yiite …ìen."
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ìe Joomi mun …ìen ka …ìe weeyata …óon, hino woodani …ìen haforaneede junuubi, e njo…ìdi mawndi ndiin woni Aljanna."